Francois BOVELL, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Daniel JUNIOR, etc., et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2601 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. DECEMBER 05, 2017 SUAREZ, LAGOA and SCALES, JJ., concur.

Following review of the emergency petition for writ of habeas corpus, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
